explanation: [0-0] A man wearing a blue tank top and black athletic shorts is jumping rope on a basketball court in a gym. The gym walls are wooden, and several people are watching him from the second floor.

[0-8] He begins to jump rope, the rope whipping quickly beneath him. He jumps higher and higher, suddenly leaping high in the air. Mid-air, he quickly curls his body, bringing his legs to his chest, the jump rope spinning rapidly at his feet. He then lands steadily, raises his head, and throws his arms up in the air to celebrate his success. As the camera zooms in, he runs to the left, jumps in the air, spreads his arms, and lands with his legs crossed. Simultaneously, the camera zooms out.
